             and the Prisoner hired him, at Strand Bridge, to carry them to the Red House at Deptford. That he carried them and waited to bring them back: That while he waited upon them, 
               <persName id="t17230116-6-person53">
                  Eleanor 
                  Clark 
               <interp inst="t17230116-6-person53" type="surname" value="Clark"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17230116-6-person53" type="given" value="Eleanor"></interp>
